O. S. KELLY et al. v. F. M. PORTER, as Receiver of CROMWELL-FRANKLIN OIL COMPANY et al. No. 1365. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 28, 1936. J. B. A. Robertson, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellants. K. W. Shartel, Lynn Adams, and John H. Miley, all of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellees.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and BRATTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, on motion'of appellees.
